T1  - Top Management Team Experiential Variety, Competitive Repertoires, and Firm Performance: Examining the Law of Requisite Variety in the 3D Printing Industry (1986–2017)
AU  - Fox, Brian C.
AU  - Simsek, Zeki
AU  - Heavey, Ciaran
Y1  - 2021/01/05
